{"tid":333584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳200內地執法人員進駐高鐵站 為「保安利益」准帶槍","createTime":"2017-07-24T02:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T11:59:24.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff26cb0633eeba205133ad03b0c9c481f279ff6","tid":333584,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:55:18.000Z","msg":"高鐵香港段一地兩檢方案預料本周公佈，預料行政會議明天將審議一地兩檢的安排，《香港01》引述消息稱，兩地政府曾商討能否讓內地人員帶槍進入西九總站，最終基於「保安利益」考慮，認為有刑事執法權，就應有相應執法裝備，尤其慎防恐怖分子，故准予擁有刑事執法權的內地人員帶槍進港，另外總站最底兩層則為內地出入境層及月台，屬內地範圍內地有最多約200名人員會進駐，分別為出入境邊防、檢疫、海關總署的人員，但他們只能留在站內劃予內地的範圍，亦要即日往返中港兩地。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指屬內地的樓層會設有多間羈留室及器械室，當中器械室即是武器庫，用以擺放槍械、警棍、手銬等。"},{"pid":"ced04f2ed4ad3c882cfbe1f0ba0e222e1f6fcf97","tid":333584,"uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/722291/xlarge/29ae23cd1a46e0117e10f8a65ac967ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F722291%2Fxlarge%2F29ae23cd1a46e0117e10f8a65ac967ae.jpg&h=d2a8db30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cd8851e62e5e01d18776bcae43bb20288746861","tid":333584,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"即係係中國法院用中國法律審判"},{"pid":"dfa5a7244b8884cd4921d01dfa5513b7602228c5","tid":333584,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"HKVDC_2017繼續叫大陸雞"},{"pid":"89bcded4d292c6a9b48be931b66afd417a754ea4","tid":333584,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"射死港豬"},{"pid":"4805c2cb8fd2400cde75b91aea6ccf315042a2a2","tid":333584,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"支那租界"},{"pid":"3eddc03f73610e77d2c93d6c411da302569fee0a","tid":333584,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HKVDC_2017繼續叫